short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Create a list of reusable url parameters.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension allows a user to create multiple parameters.
Those parameters can then be append or removed from the current tab's url.

It will request to access your historic but this is a bug from Chrome due to tabs permissions. We don't not use your historic nor access it. You still need to accept the request,
